{
  "texts": [
    "Each TLO has a name and a written description.",
    "The \"Evaluation\" element assigns a value to assess the TLO's achievement, and the TLO's scope can be further defined by an optional list of associated capabilities. 8.",
    "Evaluation: The Evaluation block outlines the evaluation criteria for a TLO.",
    "Within this block, there are three key components:-Description: This provides a textual description of the evaluation criteria.",
    "-Metrics: This comprises a list of specific metrics used to assess the TLO's achievement."
  ]
}